      "The client is seeking a talented and experienced Backend React Developer to join our dynamic team in the field of eCommerce and B2B (Business-to-Business) solutions. As a Backend React Developer, you will play a crucial role in developing and maintaining robust and scalable backend systems that power their eCommerce and B2B platforms. You will collaborate closely with their frontend developers, designers, and other cross-functional teams to ensure smooth integration and delivery of high-quality solutions.  Responsibilities • Develop and maintain scalable backend systems using React, Node.js, and other relevant technologies for our eCommerce and B2B platforms. • Collaborate with frontend developers to integrate frontend components with the backend, ensuring seamless functionality and user experience. • Design and implement RESTful APIs and other web services to facilitate data exchange between the backend systems and external partners or systems. • Develop and optimize database schemas, queries, and data models to ensure efficient data storage and retrieval. • Write clean, well-documented, and maintainable code while adhering to industry best practices and coding standards. • Conduct thorough testing and debugging of backend applications to identify and resolve issues, ensuring high-quality deliverables. • Collaborate with cross-functional teams, including product managers, designers, and QA engineers, to gather requirements and translate them into technical solutions. • Stay up to date with the latest trends and advancements in backend development and eCommerce technologies, and evaluate their potential application to improve our systems. • Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues and provide support and guidance to other team members when necessary. • Participate in code reviews, provide constructive feedback, and contribute to maintaining a positive and collaborative team environment.  Requirements • Bachelor's degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or a related field (or equivalent experience). • Proven experience as a Backend React Developer, with a focus on eCommerce and/or B2B solutions. • Strong proficiency in JavaScript, React, and Node.js. • Solid understanding of backend development principles, including server-side rendering, asynchronous programming, and RESTful architecture. • Experience with database technologies, such as SQL and NoSQL, and proficiency in writing optimized queries. • Familiarity with backend frameworks/libraries, such as Express.js or Koa, and knowledge of serverless computing is a plus. • Understanding of frontend technologies and concepts, including HTML, CSS, and responsive web design. • Knowledge of version control systems (e.g., Git) and experience with collaborative development workflows. • Experience with cloud platforms (e.g., AWS, Azure) and containerization technologies (e.g., Docker) is desirable. • Strong problem-solving skills and ability to work effectively in a fast-paced, collaborative environment. • Excellent communication skills and ability to effectively articulate technical concepts to both technical and non-technical stakeholders. If you are a passionate Backend React Developer looking for an exciting opportunity to contribute to the development of cutting-edge eCommerce and B2B solutions, we would love to hear from you. Join their team and make a significant impact on their growing business!",
